  Title: Restock
  Description: 'You can pay to have the shop restocked. Restocking the shop means
    a whole new selection of dice faces, even if you had previously purchased all
    the faces for sale! As long as you can pay, you can restock.


    But keep in
    mind, the price of a restock goes up with every consecutive purchase.'
